    # ========================================================================
    # mmb20 cross-platform retrieval (dataset: mmb0-1b_smb1-20b_1p_shared_genes)
    # ========================================================================
    # Train on 19 STARmap+ sections (mouse CNS, batches 1..14 + 16..20);
    # hold out STARmap batch 15 (within-platform baseline; matches the
